d by a stale uplift revision. a=bustage\n", "files": ["browser/components/preferences/tests/home/browser_startup_browser_restore_session.js"], "git_node": "45e4a5ac84ecffdb0688651e747c34839f85996c", "git_parents": ["28ff180211f1c80c2d208d9fad69ce31ebff4447"], "node": "19eca46b77e2aed77f161e8b8117705adbc4e680", "parents": ["1b52062fdbc52ab634ba385b9c4a000ab3d66003"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779414577, "git_changesets": ["45e4a5ac84ecffdb0688651e747c34839f85996c"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26446": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jonathan Moss \u003cjmoss@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2040479 - Support updated Azure A10 WebGL renderer string.  a=RyanVM DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301143\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301952\n", "files": ["dom/canvas/test/webgl-mochitest/test_renderer_strings.html"], "git_node": "4a96876973a14ae6c03409ad3ac1bd29c579f2c6", "git_parents": ["45e4a5ac84ecffdb0688651e747c34839f85996c"], "node": "ee8ba9dba38a9341cc00fe5cf4530ead3d529ea3", "parents": ["19eca46b77e2aed77f161e8b8117705adbc4e680"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779414784, "git_changesets": ["4a96876973a14ae6c03409ad3ac1bd29c579f2c6"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26447": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jared Hirsch \u003cohai@6a68.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2040824 - Automatically create share after completing sign in  a=RyanVM\n\n* Refactor away from the immutable share object pattern introduced in\n  bug 2025995. We first attempt to share, get the unauthorized error,\n  then prompt the user to sign in; if the user signs in successfully\n  before the timeout, we resubmit the share via fetch, then load the\n  share in a new tab when that second attempt succeeds. However, if\n  the shareResult object is immutable, then we will still have the\n  now-stale unauthorized error from the first attempt--so Firefox will\n  think the second share failed, even if it succeeded. Rather than paper\n  over the bug by checking the last error in the list of errors, it\n  seems better to simplify away the unneeded immutability properties.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301629\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301947\n", "files": ["browser/components/contentsharing/ContentSharingUtils.sys.mjs", "browser/components/contentsharing/content/content-sharing-modal.mjs", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testFeatureDisabled.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testModalErrors.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testServerErrors.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testShareBookmarks.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testShareTabGroup.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testShareTabs.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/head.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/unit/head.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/unit/test_makeValid.js", "browser/components/contentsharing/tests/unit/test_schema.js"], "git_node": "6536abc6b4a0fe49b01419567b354338d530c62f", "git_parents": ["4a96876973a14ae6c03409ad3ac1bd29c579f2c6"], "node": "0f6e82507a123b4782ecdd04ed5024b318b57113", "parents": ["ee8ba9dba38a9341cc00fe5cf4530ead3d529ea3"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779414832, "git_changesets": ["6536abc6b4a0fe49b01419567b354338d530c62f"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26448": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Import translations from main\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/protection-dashboard/src/main/res/values-ug/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-ar/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-bg/strings.xml", "mobile/