s://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301032\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303012\n", "files": ["dom/canvas/WebGLBuffer.cpp"], "git_node": "21c85f536bbb8d13e7dee555784f58f9707a0692", "git_parents": ["620455c171edb643480e554df628112415c8067e"], "node": "b98c6533cff9eb08adbb97a8d451656081160be6", "parents": ["b866b5afc55c3ffa27ebb29d282fd4f8055655ee"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Silva \u003cnical@fastmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2037323 - Update the cache in copyBufferSubData.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301065\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303013\n", "files": ["dom/canvas/WebGL2ContextBuffers.cpp"], "git_node": "d22fc5beb0fc1a9c8a5ffc14ab19b5bd0072d773", "git_parents": ["21c85f536bbb8d13e7dee555784f58f9707a0692"], "node": "e314060d175b7b28a2debfe026c53b86819c0fe2", "parents": ["b98c6533cff9eb08adbb97a8d451656081160be6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Nicolas Silva \u003cnical@fastmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2038444 - Cleanup transform feedback preparation.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301080\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303014\n", "files": ["dom/canvas/WebGLTransformFeedback.cpp", "dom/canvas/WebGLTransformFeedback.h"], "git_node": "7b3c3d678cf3cd5c663d6f68591029474191e7ab", "git_parents": ["d22fc5beb0fc1a9c8a5ffc14ab19b5bd0072d773"], "node": "37e64e741fa2b3d38420692d5e5031d668d7a67b", "parents": ["e314060d175b7b28a2debfe026c53b86819c0fe2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779973923, "git_changesets": ["21c85f536bbb8d13e7dee555784f58f9707a0692", "d22fc5beb0fc1a9c8a5ffc14ab19b5bd0072d773", "7b3c3d678cf3cd5c663d6f68591029474191e7ab"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26556": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nika Layzell \u003cnika@thelayzells.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2039873 - Simplify SharedWorker remote type handling,  a=RyanVM\n\nThis simplifies the handling of remote types for SharedWorker, by supplying the\nparent process computation with the content process remote type, and dropping\nthe content process computation.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302396\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302791\n", "files": ["dom/serviceworkers/ServiceWorkerPrivate.cpp", "dom/workers/remoteworkers/RemoteWorkerManager.cpp", "dom/workers/remoteworkers/RemoteWorkerManager.h", "dom/workers/sharedworkers/SharedWorker.cpp", "dom/workers/sharedworkers/SharedWorkerService.cpp", "dom/workers/sharedworkers/SharedWorkerService.h"], "git_node": "378f1ab2f5fc2057bd19774307089b36dfb8a46b", "git_parents": ["7b3c3d678cf3cd5c663d6f68591029474191e7ab"], "node": "0209630fe90177fe7cd4d33c58ee3cd0b74aa416", "parents": ["37e64e741fa2b3d38420692d5e5031d668d7a67b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779973952, "git_changesets": ["378f1ab2f5fc2057bd19774307089b36dfb8a46b"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26557": {"changesets": [{"author": "Emilio Cobos \u00c1lvarez \u003cemilio@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2025058 - Ensure the fullscreen element is allowed before setting it sync.  a=RyanVM\n\nIf our document is already fullscreen, we were bypassing the \"fullscreen\nelement allowed\" check, causing an \u003csvg:text\u003e element to become\nfullscreen incorrectly.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302736\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303011\n", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "testing/web-platform/tests/fullscreen/api/element-request-fullscreen-svg-text.html"], "git_node": "e431363c24213bc4b3bef2dc296357038ac99cb9", "git_parents": ["378f1ab2f5fc2057bd19774307089b36dfb8a46b"], "node": "c55db54d50533d6b585323ab4e85ca1ad3e7f09c", "parents": ["0209630fe90177fe7cd4d33c58ee3cd0b74aa416"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779973980, "git_changesets": ["e431363c24213bc4b3bef2dc296357038ac99cb9"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26558": {"changesets": [{"author": "Julian Descottes \u003cjdescottes@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041881 - [devtools] Override .browserContainer background from felt-v1 PBM in RDM  a=RyanVM DONTBUILD\n\nThe .browserContainer `background` is assigned to a linear-gradient in PBM. This commit updates the RDM css to also set the background instead of the background-color to ensure we override the default value properly.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302729\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302985\n", "files": ["devtools/client/responsive/responsive-browser.css"], "git_node": "95c5b369c1b20d72c91b04d1af86ef778520735c", "git_parents": ["e431363c24213bc4b3bef2dc296357038ac99cb9"], "node": "8ff593bbdec0965c6c426dfd859e90dc25d4361b", "parents": ["c55db54d50533d6b585323ab4e85ca1ad3e7f09c"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779974025, "git_changesets": ["95c5b369c1b20d72c91b04d1af86ef778520735c"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26559": {"changesets": [{"author": "Harshit Sohaney \u003chsohaney@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2042176 - disable backups on MacOS.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302346\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302829\n", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js"], "git_node": "0e03f6340c1cc6bc103ce41d6ad8beccee2f33e1", "git_parents": ["95c5b369c1b20d72c91b04d1af86ef778520735c"], "node": "0d39c62a03f6084073662d63abc044ebc8f3845d", "parents": ["8ff593bbdec0965c6c426dfd859e90dc25d4361b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779974086, "git_changesets": ["0e03f6340c1cc6bc103ce41d6ad8beccee2f33e1"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26560": {"changesets": [{"author": "Finn Terdal \u003cfterdal@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2040578 - Fix Share folder context menu item  a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302113\n", "files": ["browser/components/places/content/browserPlacesViews.js", "browser/components/places/content/placesContextMenu.inc.xhtml", "browser/locales/en-US/browser/places.ftl"], "git_node": "9bf250cbfd0cb65330f4092a258843ee95d2a8f7", "git_parents": ["0e03f6340c1cc6bc103ce41d6ad8beccee2f33e1"], "node": "c8a6b6691336baafced2c1819f4cfed02936d92a", "parents": ["0d39c62a03f6084073662d63abc044ebc8f3845d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779974352, "git_changesets": ["9bf250cbfd0cb65330f4092a258843ee95d2a8f7"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26561": {"changesets": [{"author": "Elissa Cha \u003cecha@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2042497 - Remove userFeedbackCollection pref gating for Smart Window feedback  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302576\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302961\n", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/components/ai-chat-content/chat-assistant-footer/assistant-message-footer.css", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/components/ai-chat-content/chat-assistant-footer/assistant-message-footer.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/test/browser/browser_aiwindow_assistant_message_footer.js"], "git_node": "8b841ef749217f6bccf47b501276b7c76334dde6", "git_parents": ["9bf250cbfd0cb65330f4092a258843ee95d2a8f7"], "node": "b3bf38a69646d67fa81e4d5e2b366dfb8cde369b", "parents": ["c8a6b6691336baafced2c1819f4cfed02936d92a"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779974392, "git_changesets": ["8b841ef749217f6bccf47b501276b7c76334dde6"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26562": {"changesets": [{"author": "Ryan VanderMeulen \u003crvandermeulen@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2040578 - Update browser_testShareFolderEmpties.js for renamed l10n id. a=bustage\n", "files": ["browser/components/contentsharing/tests/browser/browser_testShareFolderEmpties.js"], "git_node": "f78f3b8d109642e53f738da3c4c5a52485fe8265", "git_parents": ["8b841ef749217f6bccf47b501276b7c76334dde6"], "node": "94454d03a4ea617d205514de69480468c3dbfcd0", "parents": ["b3bf38a69646d67fa81e4d5e2b366dfb8cde369b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779985789, "git_changesets": ["f78f3b8d109642e53f738da3c4c5a52485fe8265"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26563": {"changesets": [{"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041705 - Surface the sports widget error card in every failure mode  a=RyanVM\n\nPreviously the error card only swapped into live match rows on a failed\nrefresh poll. Server 500s, cold-start offline, debug-toggle while offline,\nand pre-7-day refresh all hit other paths that either kept rendering stale\ndata or silently fell back to the FollowTeam / Countdown / Following promos.\n\nCloses those gaps:\n\n- WorldCupMatchesRepository: a null body from the client (returned when\n  the underlying network / API call was caught as an exception, including\n  5xx) is now a failure instead of an empty success. The middleware now\n  dispatches LoadFailed instead of an empty MatchCardStateUpdated that\n  cleared errorState as a side effect.\n- SportsWidgetMiddleware: take an isOnline lambda and short-circuit\n  fetchAndBuild to FetchFailed(ConnectionInterrupted) before invoking the\n  repository. Wired in Components.kt via ConnectivityManager.isOnline(),\n  so every dispatch site (HomeFragment, controller, debug-tool toggles,\n  Apply button, override updates) produces the right error variant without\n  its own connectivity check.\n- HomeFragment.onResume: also dispatch ConnectionInterrupted in the\n  countdown phase (pre-7-day) when offline, so cold-open offline replaces\n  the inert countdown promo with the error card.\n- SportsWidget.sportsCardPages: when errorState is set the pager always\n  leads with the error card, replacing the FollowTeam / Countdown-with-\n  Follow-CTA / Following promos. If no live match exists anywhere in\n  matchCardStates, collapse to a single error card and suppress all match\n  cards. Live matches keep MatchBody's existing in-line swap.\n- WorldCupMatchesRepositoryTest: updated for the new contract.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302140\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303097\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/Components.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/appstate/AppAction.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/appstate/sports/SportsWidgetReducer.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/HomeFragment.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/SportsWidgetMiddleware.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/WorldCupMatchesRepository.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsCardPager.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsWidget.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/components/appstate/sports/SportsWidgetReducerTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/SportsWidgetMiddlewareTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/WorldCupMatchesRepositoryTest.kt"], "git_node": "7b335f16c5187cd066040e32d997291f1c75b016", "git_parents": ["f78f3b8d109642e53f738da3c4c5a52485fe8265"], "node": "c1cb389922eb93eead103e2b21b7bf33f68173e2", "parents": ["94454d03a4ea617d205514de69480468c3dbfcd0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041811 - Update Homepage Sports Widget tool in debug drawer to work with mock server  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302142\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303098\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/debugsettings/sportswidget/SportsWidgetDebugTool.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values/static_strings.xml"], "git_node": "7c3e3de8ada375deeebe80de85f1b26c2f9dfc11", "git_parents": ["7b335f16c5187cd066040e32d997291f1c75b016"], "node": "6f54030b3501dd4e1f5f8c0b185be74119117dde", "parents": ["c1cb389922eb93eead103e2b21b7bf33f68173e2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1779988949, "git_changesets": ["7b335f16c5187cd066040e32d997291f1c75b016", "7c3e3de8ada375deeebe80de85f1b26c2f9dfc11"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26564": {"changesets": [{"author": "Duncan McIntosh \u003cdmcintosh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041416 - Compare icon data in browser_taskbarTabs_icons.js instead of just comparing dimensions.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301875\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303120\n", "files": ["browser/components/taskbartabs/test/browser/browser.toml", "browser/components/taskbartabs/test/browser/browser_taskbarTabs_icons.js"], "git_node": "a94919536cec78d5f9ee4118f5d0b335f4a84026", "git_parents": ["7c3e3de8ada375deeebe80de85f1b26c2f9dfc11"], "node": "8f992f895435086eec6225b75b3f2a2241006b65", "parents": ["6f54030b3501dd4e1f5f8c0b185be74119117dde"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Duncan McIntosh \u003cdmcintosh@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2039035 - Handle manifest icons from the manifest passed to findOrCreateTaskbarTab.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D300576\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303121\n", "files": ["browser/components/taskbartabs/TaskbarTabs.sys.mjs", "browser/components/taskbartabs/test/browser/browser_taskbarTabs_icons.js"], "git_node": "53f0e8b7fe46693d86b94b69969fe5e7ebd5a57e", "git_parents": ["a94919536cec78d5f9ee4118f5d0b335f4a84026