 configs after merge day operations a=release\n\nIGNORE BROKEN CHANGESETS\nCLOSED TREE\n", "files": ["CLOBBER", "build/defines.sh"], "git_node": "8266364660554ff30ec1f57119b07e16192af443", "git_parents": ["4e477eb4771d42033e59992fe77d0be604fc8d04"], "node": "2d6a0407cf5d1653b03fbf117f160e4ed327efbf", "parents": ["2ebcfff08969e993de614679bf8ba3879de0ec91"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780076186, "git_changesets": ["8266364660554ff30ec1f57119b07e16192af443"], "user": "ffxbld@lando.moz.tools"}, "26597": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003cffxbld@lando.moz.tools\u003e", "branch": "tags-unified", "desc": "No bug - Tagging a74e868fd1dab172ce866ff6be140f6b9ee2995d with DEVEDITION_152_0b5_RELEASE a=tagging CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": "8720a606784367813da2f1e65292c29898d0f9f7", "git_parents": ["99e65bcd6e894c898da5e629a4007e168152b5df"], "node": "5dfcf86d46a563188c24082b2ef07d35a24756b0", "parents": ["8518a811c9c647b6a5674c16976d6157fa22c353"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780077483, "git_changesets": ["8720a606784367813da2f1e65292c29898d0f9f7"], "user": "ffxbld@lando.moz.tools"}, "26598": {"changesets": [{"author": "Moyin \u003cmadeyemi@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041688 - Hide Firefox Sports logo when the sports widget is hidden  a=RyanVM\n\n{F71477898}\n\nThe previous condition only checked when the Sports Widget feature switch was enabled, and didn't check if the Sports Widget was displayed.\n\nAlso the accessibility functionality has been updated to only make the image clickable when the Sports widget is displayed, so Talkback ignores it otherwise.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303070\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303357\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/ui/Homepage.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/ui/Wordmark.kt"], "git_node": "d2eb6bf33ec4059450c56084424f795af231bb06", "git_parents": ["8266364660554ff30ec1f57119b07e16192af443"], "node": "76844a4d75f696cc30bd703d842cb5269ad44e40", "parents": ["2d6a0407cf5d1653b03fbf117f160e4ed327efbf"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780083746, "git_changesets": ["d2eb6bf33ec4059450c56084424f795af231bb06"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26599": {"changesets": [{"author": "giorga \u003cgiorga@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2042018 - Fix Crash in [@ java.lang.IllegalStateException: at androidx.fragment.app.Fragment.requireContext(Fragment.java)].  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302274\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303332\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/browser/BaseBrowserFragment.kt"], "git_node": "fa0c24fe9fc68dc1e23804d5473fea14a9fc4ee4", "git_parents": ["d2eb6bf33ec4059450c56084424f795af231bb06"], "node": "50b7edf5512c456d52d0dab21e94d20916994f92", "parents": ["76844a4d75f696cc30bd703d842cb5269ad44e40"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780083772, "git_changesets": ["fa0c24fe9fc68dc1e23804d5473fea14a9fc4ee4"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26600": {"changesets": [{"author": "Moyin \u003cmadeyemi@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041655 - Update sports widget menu to Follow your team when team is not selected  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303105\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303360\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportWidgetMenu.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsCardPager.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsWidget.kt"], "git_node": "d660d51817f3e5b5944c129a5cfda744a8e23ac0", "git_parents": ["fa0c24fe9fc68dc1e23804d5473fea14a9fc4ee4"], "node": "8ea8b49befe66326ab07ef2e599b330e8353efd4", "parents": ["50b7edf5512c456d52d0dab21e94d20916994f92"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780083798, "git_changesets": ["d660d51817f3e5b5944c129a5cfda744a8e23ac0"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26601": {"changesets": [{"author": "sarah541 \u003csarahkhan1107@hotmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2043299 - Suppress sports-widget error UI during one-week-to-kickoff phase when a cached schedule is available  a=RyanVM\n\nDuring the one-week-to-kickoff phase (isOneWeekToWorldCup), there are no\nlive scores that could be wrong \u2014 just a schedule the user has already\nseen. Collapsing the whole pager to a single SportsWidgetErrorCard on\nevery fetch failure removes useful cached content. Suppress the error UI\nin this phase when matchCardStates is non-empty; only fall back to the\nerror card when the cache is empty and the user truly has nothing else\nto look at. hasWorldCupStarted behavior is unchanged \u2014 errors there must\nstill surface, either inline-swapped on the live match or as a collapsed\nerror card if no live match is in progress.\n\nAlso promotes sportsCardPages and SportsCardPagesResult from private to\ninternal so the new behavior can be exercised by a unit-test suite that\ndoesn't require a Compose harness.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303086\n\n3m\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303349\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsWidget.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/ui/SportsWidgetTest.kt"], "git_node": "208a36cb331c1c2288a3c284186577b1074d8143", "git_parents": ["d660d51817f3e5b5944c129a5cfda744a8e23ac0"], "node": "7b8cca5004b4b45b716af9f42acee7f0d53cd484", "parents": ["8ea8b49befe66326ab07ef2e599b330e8353efd4"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780083825, "git_changesets": ["208a36cb331c1c2288a3c284186577b1074d8143"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26602": {"changesets": [{"author": "Johan Lorenzo \u003cjlorenzo@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2039863 - Fix browser_releaseNotesURL.js test failing on non-official builds  ,mossop  a=RyanVM DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301711\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303369\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/about/browser_releaseNotesURL.js"], "git_node": "4bb4a9d58e7bf41c97a0c821836934fb150a460b", "git_parents": ["208a36cb331c1c2288a3c284186577b1074d8143"], "node": "45bd3e5674fb5fcc6fbac03365618d0a57849b8b", "parents": ["7b8cca5004b4b45b716af9f42acee7f0d53cd484"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780085007, "git_changesets": ["4bb4a9d58e7bf41c97a0c821836934fb150a460b"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26603": {"changesets": [{"author": "Valentin Pollet \u003cvpollet@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041340 - Fixed condition in LlamaGenerateTask::IsActive  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301804\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303472\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/ml/backends/llama/LlamaRunner.cpp", "toolkit/components/ml/tests/browser/browser_ml_native.js"], "git_node": "923f37e4d9ae5b1b80626fa8c4ae7954ba5d864b", "git_parents": ["4bb4a9d58e7bf41c97a0c821836934fb150a460b"], "node": "d6e2311ee835269b6a204145b814462b380b7694", "parents": ["45bd3e5674fb5fcc6fbac03365618d0a57849b8b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780085036, "git_changesets": ["923f37e4d9ae5b1b80626fa8c4ae7954ba5d864b"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26604": {"changesets": [{"author": "Valentin Pollet \u003cvpollet@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2024445 - Changed MetadataCallback reference to its LlamaRunner to a weak pointer.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D300357\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303470\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/ml/backends/llama/LlamaRunner.cpp", "toolkit/components/ml/backends/llama/LlamaRunner.h"], "git_node": "39dc72769e133c03776d06bfdd3fe0508bd43498", "git_parents": ["923f37e4d9ae5b1b80626fa8c4ae7954ba5d864b"], "node": "e6228b8b888702b0ff5cf5be76bf16bcb316a9f0", "parents": ["d6e2311ee835269b6a204145b814462b380b7694"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780085063, "git_changesets": ["39dc72769e133c03776d06bfdd3fe0508bd43498"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26605": {"changesets": [{"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2023443 Part 1: Ensure ownership of external images in various WR actors.  a=RyanVM\n\nThis additionally ensures that duplicate pipeline ids are rejected by the\nWebRenderBridgeParent.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D289011\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303486\n", "files": ["gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorManagerParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/ContentCompositorBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/ImageBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/ImageBridgeParent.h", "gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderBridgeParent.h"], "git_node": "d466b29249327f2f7e0c4139a07ca46ad2451927", "git_parents": ["39dc72769e133c03776d06bfdd3fe0508bd43498"], "node": "96d11d2af4d6e6b64a28a70ed1abf973f842540d", "parents": ["e6228b8b888702b0ff5cf5be76bf16bcb316a9f0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Brad Werth \u003cbwerth@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2023443 Part 2: Add namespaces to various WR actors.  a=RyanVM\n\nThis gives CompositorBridgeParent its own namespace accessors, so the\npending bridge can be updated with the namespace from the\nCompositorManagerParent.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292650\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303487\n", "files": ["dom/ipc/ContentChild.cpp", "dom/ipc/ContentParent.cpp", "gfx/ipc/GPUParent.cpp", "gfx/ipc/GPUParent.h", "gfx/ipc/GPUProcessManager.cpp", "gfx/ipc/GPUProcessManager.h", "gfx/ipc/PGPU.ipdl", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorBridgeParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorManagerChild.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorManagerParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/CompositorManagerParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/ContentCompositorBridgeParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/ImageBridgeChild.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/ImageBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/layers/ipc/ImageBridgeParent.h", "gfx/layers/ipc/PCompositorManager.ipdl", "gfx/layers/wr/WebRenderBridgeParent.cpp", "gfx/vr/ipc/VRManagerChild.cpp", "gfx/vr/ipc/VRManagerChild.h", "gfx/vr/ipc/VRManagerParent.cpp", "gfx/vr/ipc/VRManagerParent.h"], "git_node": "c3f888b7998ad256ce7540ac651719b066418176", "git_parents": ["d466b29249327f2f7e0c4139a07ca46ad2451927"], "node": "975f2b53f4e707705d89cab8c73be6d301bd39ea", "parents": ["96d11d2af4d6e6b64a28a70ed1abf973f842540d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780085174, "git_changesets": ["d466b29249327f2f7e0c4139a07ca46ad2451927", "c3f888b7998ad256ce7540ac651719b066418176"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26606": {"changesets": [{"author": "ffxbld \u003cffxbld@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug, mozilla-beta repo-update HSTS HPKP -  a=RyanVM\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303497\n", "files": ["security/manager/ssl/StaticHPKPins.h", "security/manager/ssl/nsSTSPreloadList.inc"], "git_node": "fab10f70d4d9ba2b150abf5f39e4c69087845fed", "git_parents": ["c3f888b7998ad256ce7540ac651719b066418176"], "node": "6a84654dc1d5187715e9948cb1f3543bf1e43d36", "parents": ["975f2b53f4e707705d89cab8c73be6d301bd39ea"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780087551, "git_changesets": ["fab10f70d4d9ba2b150abf5f39e4c69087845fed"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26607": {"changesets": [{"author": "David Rubino \u003cdrubino@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2038097 - Decouple default Windows launch-on-login from stub-installer first-startup path.  a=RyanVM\n\nThe \"default Windows launch on login\" feature was registered as a\nfirst-startup-new-profile task, which only runs from the stub\ninstaller's --first-startup path. Full installer, MSI, MSIX, and zip\ninstalls never hit it, leaving the new-install default silently off\nfor those users.\n\nThis change introduces a default-true pref\n(browser.startup.windowsLaunchOnLogin.defaultEnabled) and moves the\nregistry write into StartupOSIntegration.onStartupIdle(), gated on:\n\n  - profileService.isFirstRun (new getter exposed from\n    nsToolkitProfileService.cpp via nsIToolkitProfileService.idl)\n  - browser.startup.windowsLaunchOnLogin.defaultEnabled\n  - WindowsLaunchOnLogin.getLaunchOnLoginApproved() (Windows policy)\n\nDefaultWindowsLaunchOnLogin still runs from first-startup-new-profile\nbut now writes the pref bidirectionally based on Nimbus rather than\ncalling createLaunchOnLogin() itself, preserving the ability to opt\nexperiment branches in or out via Nimbus.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D299301\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303429\n", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js", "browser/components/BrowserComponents.manifest", "browser/components/defaultwindowslaunchonlogin/DefaultWindowsLaunchOnLogin.sys.mjs", "browser/components/defaultwindowslaunchonlogin/tests/test_nimbus_defaultWindowsLaunchOnLogin_firstStartup.js", "browser/components/preferences/tests/browser_windows_launch_on_login_msix.js", "browser/components/shell/StartupOSIntegration.sys.mjs", "browser/components/shell/test/unit/test_maybeCreateLaunchOnLoginOnFirstRun.js", "browser/components/shell/test/unit/xpcshell.toml", "toolkit/profile/nsIToolkitProfileService.idl", "toolkit/profile/nsToolkitProfileService.cpp"], "git_node": "cb8aa0284a5e6a3c8a960c7b19d146b14c23b6db", "git_parents": ["fab10f70d4d9ba2b150abf5f39e4c69087845fed"], "node": "f09191bbf0fd9437abcccc73495039118b9c94fd", "parents": ["6a84654dc1d5187715e9948cb1f3543bf1e43d36"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780087578, "git_changesets": ["cb8aa0284a5e6a3c8a960c7b19d146b14c23b6db"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26608": {"changesets": [{"author": "Valentin Gosu \u003cvalentin.gosu@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2038887 - Use old error page for TRR mode 3 errors  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D301283\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303344\n", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/about/browser_aboutNetError_telemetry.js", "browser/base/content/test/about/browser_aboutNetError_trr.js", "toolkit/content/net-error-card.mjs"], "git_node": "12cea9d569b8a3bcc300eefe41f524e0574affe4", "git_parents": ["cb8aa0284a5e6a3c8a960c7b19d146b14c23b6db"], "node": "09019823883dbf3b56120c0c07bc616ed2032170", "parents": ["f09191bbf0fd9437abcccc73495039118b9c94fd"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780087606, "git_changesets": ["12cea9d569b8a3bcc300eefe41f524e0574affe4"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26609": {"changesets": [{"author": "Moyin \u003cmadeyemi@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2043585 - Accept nullable teams from the API  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303339\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303482\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/MatchCardBuilder.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/MatchesResponseMapper.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/SportsMatch.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/SportsWidgetMiddleware.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/api/SportsDto.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/MatchCardBuilderTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/test/java/org/mozilla/fenix/home/sports/MatchesResponseMapperTest.kt"], "git_node": "a95f7e8ec13ded1bf198385ae29d4fd3e3fb575a", "git_parents": ["12cea9d569b8a3bcc300eefe41f524e0574affe4"], "node": "a638f92298a2b8fbc071fef9d71a716378241bad", "parents": ["09019823883dbf3b56120c0c07bc616ed2032170"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780096605, "git_changesets": ["a95f7e8ec13ded1bf198385ae29d4fd3e3fb575a"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26610": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nathan Barrett \u003cnbarrett@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2041213 - Add New badge to tab group and bookmark folder share items.  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D302657\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303342\n", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js", "browser/base/content/main-popupset.js", "browser/components/places/content/browserPlacesViews.js", "browser/components/tabbrowser/content/tabbrowser.js", "browser/components/tabbrowser/content/tabgroup-menu.js"], "git_node": "31db8f838838aa35c6b756c82dc4663ad31ef9ea", "git_parents": ["a95f7e8ec13ded1bf198385ae29d4fd3e3fb575a"], "node": "bd613a4e5a8076886f49dae4df750e372b068dd3", "parents": ["a638f92298a2b8fbc071fef9d71a716378241bad"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780096634, "git_changesets": ["31db8f838838aa35c6b756c82dc4663ad31ef9ea"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26611": {"changesets": [{"author": "Stephen Thompson \u003csthompson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2042532 - tabsOpenInTopWindow targeting attribute  a=RyanVM\n\nReturns the number of tabs open in the top browser window.\n\nThis is analogous to the `currentTabsOpens` context targeting attribute available on a few triggers in ASRouterTriggerListeners, but is available globally.\n\nThe main motivation for this is to target a new New Tab promo message to users who have more than 8 tabs open in their current window. The intention is for this targeting attribute to be more generally useful, though.\n\nThis only reports about the top window. Future work would be required to add a tab count that covers all windows.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303102\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303381\n", "files": ["browser/components/asrouter/docs/targeting-attributes.md", "browser/components/asrouter/modules/ASRouterTargeting.sys.mjs", "browser/components/asrouter/tests/browser/browser_asrouter_targeting.js"], "git_node": "024232715f7f3e2d883bc8b3c7aa7ca8b8f32380", "git_parents": ["31db8f838838aa35c6b756c82dc4663ad31ef9ea"], "node": "7f8351c5b41ef672501eef9b96070748d0ca037b", "parents": ["bd613a4e5a8076886f49dae4df750e372b068dd3"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780096660, "git_changesets": ["024232715f7f3e2d883bc8b3c7aa7ca8b8f32380"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26612": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jeff Muizelaar \u003cjmuizelaar@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2043413 - Avoid sending null data to NewArrayBufferWithUserOwnedContents()  a=RyanVM\n\nNewArrayBufferWithUserOwnedContents asserts that the data parameter\nis not null. Instead of passing null just create an emtpy ArrayBuffer.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303198\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303423\n", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/jsapi/RTCEncodedFrameBase.cpp"], "git_node": "4c437e8f21f5743be7897a5ffcff595e631e504c", "git_parents": ["024232715f7f3e2d883bc8b3c7aa7ca8b8f32380"], "node": "b200bfcc6b90f897adb73bf347bbd04c7148913d", "parents": ["7f8351c5b41ef672501eef9b96070748d0ca037b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780096686, "git_changesets": ["4c437e8f21f5743be7897a5ffcff595e631e504c"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26613": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nathan Barrett \u003cnbarrett@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2043437 - Add contentsharing feature manifest entry  a=RyanVM\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303224\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D303341\n", "files": ["toolkit/components/nimbus/FeatureManifest.yaml"], "git_node": "f6d28d2e94bee2d7d3a62aac55411220d024609d", "git_parents": ["4c437e8f21f5743be7897a5ffcff595e631e504c"], "node": "e0c2f89a0167cc500215de5266c852c247f93966", "parents": ["b200bfcc6b90f897adb73bf347bbd04c7148913d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1780096712, "git_changesets": ["f6d28d2e94bee2d7d3a62aac55411220d024609d"], "user": "rvandermeulen@mozilla.com"}, "26614": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Import translations from main\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/compose/base/src/main/res/values-bqi/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/app-links/src/main/res/values-bqi/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/app-links/src/main/res/values-fy-rNL/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/app-links/src/main/res/values-zh-rCN/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/app-links/src/main/res/values-zh-rTW/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/longfox/src/main/res/values-fy-rNL/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/longfox/src/main/res/values-zh-rCN/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/longfox/src/main/res/values-zh-rTW/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-ar/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-el/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-fy-rNL/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-nb-rNO/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-nl/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-ru/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/values-zh-rCN/strings.xml", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/res/va